    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good summary. i was thinking about the climate side of it though—since most experts say it's one of the fastest ways to hit carbon reduction goals, does that make the opposition's arguments about cost seem kind of outdated or even counterproductive to the bigger picture?",
